# Web3-Frontier Conventions

- pnpm workspace monorepo. Use `pnpm` only (never `npm`/`yarn`).
- Node 20+ and TypeScript (strict) across all packages.
- Layout will be `apps/cli`, `apps/web`, `packages/shared`, `packages/brand`. Don’t create a top-level root `src/`.
- Solana-only. Use `@solana/web3.js` (no EVM libraries in v1).
- Never log or print secret keys, mnemonics, passphrases, or raw keystore contents.
- Any state-changing tool must do simulate + show summary + require explicit user confirmation before signing/sending.
- All CLI output must support `--plain` mode and respect `NO_COLOR`.
- Do not create any README files unless the user explicitly asks.
